items.postText: Ali Shahriyar A: "Abul shaab: on Ashuraful return issue: ODI average 22 in 177 ODIs and Test average 24 in 61 Tests, is it a stats for a 'potential World Class" player ? And about 'handling him badly'.. BD told him to involve in match-fixing ? After his ban lifted, the door is open for him, he just needs to score plenty of runs to get back to the team....BD dont have the luxury to have a mid 20 average player now. Even players like Tamim Shakib are being criticized if they dont score 50 in every 3-4 innings."
